<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-15"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-15')">15</a>. Fuck. ~ Esther</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-16"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-16')">16</a>. If these guys are so into logic like has been stated, then why can't we just try to reason with them? ~ Cycloid</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-17"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-17')">17</a>. Maybe if they weren't fascists, Cycloid. But it's like drawing blood from a stone with them. ~Esther</div>
